0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.0c28a345-f435-4cfe-8a09-9b481fccf24c.prompt=Enter password\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.104f25c8-dd12-42fc-bb4e-bea47d5c7b86.prompt=Enter password\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.18f53f4a-27f5-42bd-987c-e16a671affbb.prompt=Root DN\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.19c13cae-bff2-4115-8154-3c7f86865e16.prompt=Enter host\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.229ca60c-0ce9-4466-ac28-8b3b0acf69cc.description=
Deletes a user from Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username.
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the user that should be deleted is in
userCommonName - the CN, generally the full name of user (i.e. Bob Smith)


Responses\:
success - user was successfully deleted
failure - failed to delete user

Extra Results\:
userDN - The distinguinsed name of the user that was deleted.
0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.28679895-883d-47be-a149-8654c6e01545.prompt=Enter host\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.2af2e89d-f14e-4a75-879d-159955ec92f1.prompt=Username\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.2ca31148-944d-463b-8f9f-24d551c7b308.prompt=Enter userPassword\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.2e92210e-576c-4bdb-8bbd-391afbba0b36.prompt=Enter password\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.34ada891-7fb3-4dd3-89a7-5096eb49b968.prompt=Enter new userPassword\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.37c56b70-c110-4bd6-81bc-b4ccc28396d0.description=
Enables a user account in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the user is in (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
userCommonName - the name of the user (its CN)
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Responses\:
success - user was successfully enabled
failure - something went wrong

Extra Results\:
userDN - The distinguinsed name of the user that was enabled.
0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.3b6f2a1e-cf51-4631-be28-6338acee4c88.prompt=Host\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.44bab998-f76c-4396-83b6-b185db20cbd9.prompt=Enter host\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.468a8b0f-fb71-4465-ba37-68f7ea419457.prompt=Enter password\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.59427c17-c14c-4544-8f4c-85755d8f2279.prompt=Enter computer Distinguished Name(DN)\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.5f785ee7-1282-4807-a7ee-09fc525d504c.prompt=Enter username\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.63bf4420-952d-4b7d-bd5f-82fb2e44c6fa.prompt=Enter username\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.63e07bf3-2609-47ca-a333-62f9a17ff484.description=
Resets a users password in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - hostname or IP Address of AD Server
userDN - distinguished name of the user whose password you want to change
userPassword - the new password
username - account with admin privlidges or reset password privlidges in domain
password - password to admin account

Responeses\:
success - password has been reset
failure - failed to reset password
0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.65318417-e3f3-490d-91cc-3d73bdc978f4.prompt=Enter user Common Name(CN)\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.6dd2caba-3c52-4a49-8d39-5ef22e57c283.prompt=Enter password\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.715bb688-c123-4584-84c0-1f5a3ff414c2.prompt=Enter password\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.71fbfd81-33bf-4acb-947b-558b27519f8e.prompt=Enter OU's Distinguished Name(DN)\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.769a3d3c-4cfe-44c1-8bdb-d51d62aedd6b.prompt=Enter user Common Name(CN)\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.84765756-19c5-4285-be2f-41e5adb00676.prompt=Enter username\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.8bee5e67-b755-4b76-a66b-d62d183dbf4d.description=
Checks to see if a user account is enabled in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - The domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the user is in (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
userCommonName - The name of the user to check
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Responses\:
success - The user is enabled
failure - The user is disabled or something went wrong

Extra Results\:
userDN - The distinguinsed name of the user.
0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.905523b3-83ca-4643-9bab-79f15b579d73.prompt=Enter username\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.96d3b682-7316-4b0f-9a06-4d68cbc00f81.prompt=Enter username\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.9ab9fa5b-43a9-4a7e-95b1-511373c91ff3.prompt=Enter host\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.ae545fff-5354-4a2e-8991-a4544c294565.description=
Authenticates a user against Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - The hostname or IP address of the AD server.
rootDN - The distinguished name of the root element whose subtree you want to search in (e.g. CN\=Users,DC\=domain,DC\=com).
username - The user's windows username. The only valid format is domain\username.
password - The user's password.

Responses\:
success - User authenticated against AD.
failure - User could not be authenticated.
0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.bd794918-82d2-480b-931b-bbbde59265cc.prompt=Enter OU's Distinguished Name(DN)\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.c0ed07d6-5579-4565-bf96-dab6ad28a462.prompt=Enter user Common Name(CN)\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.c6818ef9-7b95-45ea-86ef-f4a2f1705521.description=
Disables a user account in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the user is in (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
userCommonName - the name of the user (its CN)
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Responses\:
success - user was successfully disabled
failure - something went wrong

Extra Results\:
userDN - The distinguinsed name of the user that was disabled.
0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.c7ed600a-beda-4fd0-aec4-1a1cfbdb2959.prompt=Enter sAMAccountName\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.c8836144-4ea9-4f85-a850-503e254f2630.prompt=Enter OU's Distinguished Name(DN)\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.d2e3e16a-a2e5-4e4f-89d8-46456a625f6f.prompt=Enter OU's Distinguished Name(DN)\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.d4421a6c-58ad-49ae-a883-2573e91f7bee.prompt=Enter user Common Name(CN)\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.d7db6500-1c0d-4ca4-8bbc-f5cd016748e0.description=
Creates a new user in Active Directory.

Input Parameters\:
host - domain controller
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN to add the user to (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
userCommonName - the CN, generally the full name of user (i.e. Bob Smith)
userPassword - password for user
sAMAccountName - the sAMAccountName
username - user to connect to AD as
password - password to connect to AD as

Responses\:
success - created new user in AD
failure - failed to create user

Extra Results\:
userDN - the distinguished name of the newly created user
0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.da568b68-2ad1-4dcd-b98e-978f5faec900.prompt=Enter username\: 0c5eb7bb-8681-4ccd-8c06-5c1aba1abd25.description=
Authenticates the user, creates a new user account in Active Directory, performs some operations on it (disables and enables it, resets it password) and then deletes it.

Input Parameters\:
host - domain controller
rootDN - the distinguished name of the root element whose subtree you want to search in
OU - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN to add the user to (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
userCommonName - the CN, generally the full name of user (i.e. Bob Smith)
sAMAccountName - the sAMAccountName
userPassword - password for user (must be at least 5 characters long)
username - user to connect to AD as
password - password to connect to AD as

Responses\:
success - all operations finished successfully
failure - failed to do some operation
